-- Egypt’s Eastern Given 3 Months to Introduce Watermarks, Mal Says
-- B y   A h m e d   A .   N a m a t a l l a
-- 2012-01-17T08:41:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-17/egypt-s-eastern-given-3-months-to-introduce-watermarks-mal-says.html
Eastern Co. (EAST) , Egypt’s monopoly
cigarette producer, has been granted three months to implement a
watermark system to combat counterfeit products,  Al Mal 
reported, citing Fathy Abdelaziz, who heads the information unit
at the country’s tax authority.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ahmed A Namatalla in Cairo at 
